title: For Sale:  Troy AK integrated top rail / gas piston tube. Similar to Ultimak
postcontent:
This is the new Troy top rail with integrated gas tube. It's similar to an Ultimak top rail/piston tube. However, unlike an Ultimak or other AK top rail systems, it does not need to be clamped or bolted down to the barrel or bottom rail. 

It uses a unique adjustable castle nut retention type method for retaining tension. This allows this to fit on just about every type of AK variant rifle or clone out there.

This one is brand new in box. I ordered this and the Troy long AK bottom rail, only to find that their long bottom rails don't fit certain AKs with the Bulgarian style FSB. Returned the bottom rail and kept this top rail, but deciding to sell it since I've decided to stick with the original Arsenal handguards for the time being due to not running any optics with the AK.

I installed the gas tube rail for fitting and then removed it. Has not had any rounds through it or even had the gas piston cycled through it. It's new in box.

This will fit with just about any lower handguard or rail. This is pretty much a railed gas tube like an Ultimak.

These go for $145 + shipping new online.  Asking $120 for this and will not go lower.  Prefer face to face exchange in OKC area.  Comes in original packaging new.
